70.9589, 170.8558, 171.432, 170.4069, 171.7258, 171.422, 170.7697, 170.712, 171.1516, 170.3162, 170.1026, 169.8816, 170.2468, 170.1314, 169.7767, 169.2171, 169.1606, 168.4823, 168.7596, 168.2331, 168.6596, 169.1861, 170.1505, 171.2566, 171.0564, 170.1764, 171.6823, 173.1311, 173.7064, 174.3731, 174.2351, 174.3057, 174.2174, 174.8071, 173.5726, 173.7386, 174.1975, 174.857, 173.9871, 173.9448, 173.0257, 173.6787, 175.5427, 176.5295, 175.7339, 175.7324, 178.5142, 177.3951, 177.6806, 178.4914, 179.5807, 179.1296, 179.9724, 180.1315, 180.3202, 180.901, 181.6772, 182.1349, 182.6693, 182.8676, 182.278, 182.6321, 183.2612, 182.7928, 183.4563, 184.135, 184.8173, 184.3832, 184.7635, 185.2373, 184.0773, 183.6602, 184.0455, 184.5435, 185.8717, 186.6889, 187.1245, 189.3443, 189.1722, 189.378, 188.4369, 189.8513, 189.988, 189.4155, 190.0753, 189.7964, 190.2132, 189.2761, 190.5957, 189.5374, 189.4647, 189.6448, 189.5943, 188.5741, 188.0156, 187.2027, 187.509, 187.9594, 187.3101, 188.145, 188.0299, 189.5097, 189.3692, 189.6466, 189.5146, 189.613, 191.2478, 191.7579, 191.7576, 191.0848, 189.9969, 189.6892, 189.1915, 188.9961, 189.5115, 189.8062, 189.989, 191.7453, 192.5338, 192.9658, 193.2818, 191.888, 191.8533, 194.3615, 195.0017, 197.0343, 199.113, 199.4172, 198.4977, 198.7527, 198.9183, 196.4325, 192.6051, 193.0259, 194.027, 193.8887, 194.7414, 194.5223, 195.0352, 196.3597, 194.6706, 197.1893, 197.6567, 196.8867, 196.5567, 197.4279, 199.3698, 200.5426, 200.6515, 201.0328, 200.6372, 198.6674, 202.9055, 198.1027, 195.7468, 197.2421, 196.81, 196.3849, 195.9021, 197.9954, 195.6122, 195.4359, 195.2758, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>商品基本面因子探索之甲醇 — 库存z-score反转因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报梳理了甲醇产业链基本面因子（供应/需求/库存/价差四大类），发现生产利润和库存对价格有显著的约束作用。核心交易逻辑是：计算基本面因子的滚动z-score，当z-score偏离到极端水平时反向开仓（均值回归），z-score回归正常后平仓。将此逻辑推广到全品种商品期货，库存因子（inventory_21）表现最优，因为库存极端偏高的品种往往面临供应过剩压力导致价格下跌，反之库存极低则供需紧张支撑价格上涨。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.3</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.71</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.18 / 1.41</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.33</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.87</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td>1.45</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.05</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.1</span></td><td>0.56</td><td>1.61</td><td>1.7</td><td>0.91</td><td>0.9</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.32</span></td><td>1.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>52.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>24.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>库存z-score信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_t^i = \\frac{I_t^i - \\bar{I}_{t-W:t}^i}{\\sigma_{I_{t-W:t}}^i}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">I_t^i</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的库存（inventory_21），<span class=\"math-tex\">W=200</span> 为滚动窗口。</p>\n<p>持仓信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = \\begin{cases} -1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &gt; \\theta \\text{ (库存极高→做空)} \\\\ +1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &lt; -\\theta \\text{ (库存极低→做多)} \\\\ \\text{前值} &amp; \\text{otherwise (持仓不变)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>当 <span class=\"math-tex\">|z_t^i| &lt; \\theta/2</span> 时平仓（z-score回归中性）。<span class=\"math-tex\">\\theta=1.0</span> 为入场阈值。</p>\n<p>仓位经过 vol_target_scale（目标年化波动率15%）缩放后输出。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>10个变体，inv_zscore_raw Sharpe 1.10最优；TS IC=0.023，信号有效</td><td>初始实现全部因子：时序z-score反转(利润/库存) + 截面排名(利润/库存/基差/ry) + 综合组合</td><td>Sharpe 1.10，所有gate通过</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>对库存z-score取反后传入helper导致信号方向翻转</td><td>错误：pre-negate z-score后reversal helper双重取反，27个库存变体全部负Sharpe</td><td>Sharpe降至0.73 (basis_rank)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R3</strong></td><td>修复信号方向，保持helper内部方向判断 + 参数网格(3 window x 3 threshold x 3 hold) + IC gate</td><td>修复reversal方向，添加27个参数组合 + 2个IC gate变体</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.31</strong>，14个变体&gt;0.8，决策skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R2 的信号方向错误暴露了 z-score reversal 中方向处理的微妙性——库存作为负向因子，必须在 helper 内部处理方向（高z→做空），而非预先取反后调用通用 reversal。R3 修正后 Sharpe 从 0.73 提升到 1.31。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（59个品种有效），最佳盈利品种：CF、FG、RB、SI、AP</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 中长期（z-score极端到回归需数周至数月），hold_days=10</li>\n<li><strong>数据依赖</strong>: inventory_21字段（库存21日口径），非空率~54%，部分品种/日期无数据</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 研报原文针对甲醇单品种，推广到全品种后利润因子效果弱（profit Sharpe仅0.24）\n<p>- 截面IC偏低（0.01），策略主要依赖时序信号而非截面排序 - 2018年yearly Sharpe接近0，该年基本面因子整体失效</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>EXIT_THR</code></td><td><code>0.5</code></td><td>ENTRY_THR / 2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.17s</li>\n</ul>"}